<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">君子于役</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonfe6a8d52e5ad">
君子于役，不知其期，曷至哉？鸡栖于埘，日之夕矣，羊牛下来。君子于役，如之何勿思！<br />君子于役，不日不月，曷其有佸？鸡栖于桀，日之夕矣，羊牛下括。君子于役，苟无饥渴！
</div>
</div>
